## âš¡ Realtime WebSocket Logic

1. Candidate connects â†’ server sends greeting.
2. Bot (Gemini) sends the first question.
3. Candidate replies â†’ message logged â†’ AI evaluates.
4. Score updates streamed live (WebSocket `send_json`).
5. Once complete â†’ bot sends final report, marks `status='scored'`.

